data.title: Taylor Lautner thought Kanye West interrupting Taylor Swift at 2009 MTV VMAs was 'a skit'

data.text: During the infamous moment, the singer was in the middle of her acceptance speech for Best Female Video when the rapper stormed the stage, took her microphone and declared that Beyoncé had one of the best music videos of all time.
